  of just en as per standards. Uncompress kwave.svgz and update icon cache.

  14 May 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> kwave-0.8.2.ebuild:
  If LINGUAS is unset, set it to en to avoid compilation failure.

